    "description": "A painting by Gustav Klimt that depicts a woman in gold, who despite her luxurious attire, does not seem impressed or happy. She appears indifferent and a bit sad. This painting is a central theme in my blocked page \"Congratulations, You've Struck Gold!\".",
    "author": "Gustav Klimt",
